       }\n      ],\n      \"direction\":\"ltr\",\n      \"format\":\"\",\n      \"indent\":0,\n      \"type\":\"root\",\n      \"version\":1\n   }\n}','2022-03-01 00:00:00',NULL,NULL,'[{\"lat\":6.924381939880826,\"lng\":79.85139825477901}]',5,1,NULL,'Colombo\'s very own urban fishing cats.','[\"2022\\/12\\/121220221718326397626890642.png\"]'),(15,'2022-12-13 16:26:15','2022-12-13 16:26:15',2,0,24,1,'Introduction to Project Management','introductiontoprojectmanagement6398a7a72c715',NULL,'{\n   \"root\":{\n      \"children\":[\n         {\n            \"children\":[\n               {\n                  \"detail\":0,\n                  \"format\":0,\n                  \"mode\":\"normal\",\n                  \"style\":\"\",\n                  \"text\":\"Project Management Overview through an Environmental Conservation Lens; a presentation carried out as part of FEO\'s CBO capacity building sessions around the country. This lecture entails discussion of fundamental Project Management concepts and tools with an emphasis on the management of Environmental Projects.  The material is organized focusing on developing the knowledge and skills for NGOs and CBOs who will write proposals for Small Grant Projects. Presentation Video Link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9ko6kMbAujM&t=992s\",\n                  \"type\":\"text\",\n                  \"version\":1\n               }\n            ],\n            \"direction\":\"ltr\",\n            \"format\":\"\",\n            \"indent\":0,\n            \"type\":\"paragraph\",\n            \"version\":1\n         }\n      ],\n      \"direction\":\"ltr\",\n      \"format\":\"\",\n      \"indent\":0,\n      \"type\":\"root\",\n      \"version\":1\n   }\n}','2022-12-13 00:00:00',NULL,'null','[{\"lat\":6.907340702276085,\"lng\":79.88208559245273},{\"lat\":7.472091723623534,\"lng\":80.74002127325106}]',5,1,NULL,'Project Management Overview through an Environmental Conservation Lens','[]'),(16,'2022-12-13 16:28:01','2022-12-13 16:28:01',2,0,15,1,'Conscious Consumerism - a presentation by Vraîe Cally Balthazaar.','consciousconsumerism-apresentationbyvraîecallybalthazaar.6398a811cb77c',NULL,'{\n   \"root\":{\n      \"children\":[\n         {\n            \"children\":[\n               {\n                  \"detail\":0,\n                  \"format\":0,\n                  \"mode\":\"normal\",\n                  \"style\":\"\",\n                  \"text\":\"This webinar explores the personal journey of learning to live consciously and understanding the impact of our everyday choices. Vraîe is a social entrepreneur and the owner of Cally Reusable Bags, a line of environmentally sustainable reusable bags that provides an alternative to single-use polythene and plastic. She is also an advocate of conscious consumerism, sharing her own journey of a constantly evolving lifestyle. A Webinar presentation by ENVFORCE - The FEO Youth Alliance. Presentation Video Link: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-cIh2Mdjf2M&t=66s\",\n                  \"type\":\"text\",\n                  \"version\":1\n               }\n            ],\n            \"direction\":\"ltr\",\n            \"format\":\"\",\n            \"indent\":0,\n            \"type\":\"paragraph\",\n            \"version\":1\n         }\n      ],\n      \"direction\":\"ltr\",\n      \"format\":\"\",\n      \"indent\":0,\n      \"type\":\"root\",\n      \"version\":1\n   }\n}',NULL,NULL,'null','[{\"lat\":6.989133016574015,\"lng\":79.9314486280242}]',5,1,NULL,'Personal journey of learning to live consciously and understanding the impact of our everyday choices','[]'),(17,'2022-12-13 16:34:37','2022-12-13 16:34:37',2,0,15,1,'Video collaboration with ROAR Media; Sustainable and Conscious Shopping!','videocollaborationwithroarmedia;sustainableandconsciousshopping!6398a99d0c823',NULL,'{\n   \"root\":{\n      \"children\":[\n         {\n            \"children\":[\n               {\n                  \"detail\":0,\n                  \"format\":0,\n                  \"mode\":\"normal\",\n                  \"style\":\"\",\n                  \"text\":\"As a part of their sustainable consumption campaign, FEO collaborated with ROAR media to create an awareness video which was launched in August 2022. The more informed and mindful the consumer; the more attention we would consequently pay to build a sound, planet-friendly lifestyle with our future generations in mind. Happy shopping!!! Video Campaign Link: https://www.facebook.com/feosrilanka/videos/477140754227367\",\n                  \"type\":\"text\",\n                  \"version\":1\n               }\n            ],\n            \"direction\":\"ltr\",\n            \"format\":\"\",\n            \"indent\":0,\n            \"type\":\"paragraph\",\n            \"version\":1\n         }\n      ],\n      \"direction\":\"ltr\",\n      \"format\":\"\",\n      \"indent\":0,\n      \"type\":\"root\",\n      \"version\":1\n   }\n}','2022-08-15 00:00:00','2022-08-15 00:00:00',NULL,'[{\"lat\":6.889617163817551,\"lng\":79.86790860919015}]',5,1,NULL,'FEO collaborated with ROAR media to create an awareness video','[]'),(18,'2022-12-13 16:37:00','2022-12-13 16:37:00',2,0,24,1,'Introduction to Proposal Writing','introductiontoproposalwriting6398aa2cd79c4',NULL,'{\n   \"root\":{\n      \"children\":[\n         {\n            \"children\":[\n               {\n                  \"detail\":0,\n                  \"format\":0,\n                  \"mode\":\"normal\",\n                  \"style\":\"\",\n                  \"text\":\"Proposal Writing Overview through an Environmental Conservation Lens, a presentation conducted as part of FEOs capacity building sessions for CBOs around the country. This lecture entails discussion of fundamental Proposal Writing with an emphasis on the management of Environmental Projects. The material is organized focusing on developing the knowledge and skills for NGOs and CBOs who will write proposals for Small Grant Projects.\",\n                  \"type\":\"text\",\n       